<div id="desc" class='box'><center>I am a tiny tiny researcher in love with stars and how they twinkle, how things fall into each-other, and how spacetime bends.<br>
Also fond of cats, shooting off to other sides of the world, and whatever creative pursuit is currently capturing my interests.<br>
Wanting to follow my curiosity into scientific research, particularly in gravitational wave astrophysics, and tell stories through the wobbles of the universe! Want to make physics a more comfortable place, EDI work, also occasional leanings into exoplanets and dynamical systems.
<br>
</div>

</center>


<div id="profilepic">
    <img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/76d2391d516cbc7bd6f86d50831fc048/a1f50bf5bccaa44b-bb/s1280x1920/bebc05da4dc567529b8c7b4c949ac6eadbb9a319.jpg"/>
